                  </div>
                  Regular Updates
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Receive timely updates to address bugs, enhance features, and maintain compatibility with evolving technologies.</dd>
              </div>
              
              <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                  <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-yellow-400">
                    <svg width="800px" height="800px" viewBox="0 0 48 48" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <defs>
                          <style>.a{fill:none;stroke:white;stroke-width:3;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;}</style>
                      </defs>
                      <path class="a" d="M22.2,4.86,6.69,11.25V27C6.69,35.44,24,43.5,24,43.5S41.31,35.44,41.31,27V11.25L25.8,4.86A4.68,4.68,0,0,0,22.2,4.86Z"/>
                      <polygon class="a" points="30.45 20.7 24 20.7 24 11.78 17.69 25 24.14 25 24.14 33.92 30.45 20.7"/>
                  </svg>                  </div>
                  Security Patching
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Protect your software from vulnerabilities with our proactive approach to security patching.</dd>
              </div>
              
              <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                  <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-yellow-400">
                    <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="white" aria-hidden="true">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0l3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0013.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0113.803-3.7l3.181 3.182m0-4.991v4.99" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  Performance Optimization
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">We continuously optimize code for improved performance, responsiveness, and scalability.</dd>
              </div>

              <div class="relative pl-16">
                <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-gray-900">
                  <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-yellow-400">
                    <svg width="800px" height="800px" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M6 1C4.34314 1 3 2.34315 3 4V20C3 21.6569 4.34315 23 6 23H19C20.6569 23 22 21.6569 22 20V10C22 9.73478 21.8946 9.48043 21.7071 9.29289L13.7071 1.29292C13.6114 1.19722 13.4983 1.1229 13.3753 1.07308C13.2572 1.02527 13.1299 1 13 1H6ZM12 3H6C5.44771 3 5 3.44771 5 4V20C5 20.5523 5.44772 21 6 21H19C19.5523 21 20 20.5523 20 20V11H13C12.4477 11 12 10.5523 12 10V3ZM18.5858 9.00003L14 4.41424V9.00003H18.5858Z" fill="white"/>
                  </svg>
                  </div>
                  Documentation
                </dt>
                <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600">Access comprehensive documentation for troubleshooting, configuration, and best practices.</dd>
              </div>
              
             
            </dl>
          </div>
